{"tid":754050,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"約左精神科 好驚啊","createTime":"2018-07-24T06:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T15:44:15.000Z","uid":85420,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c5efea4c9208c93ed4e22895786954a5a3ea1215","tid":754050,"uid":85420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T06:04:35.000Z","msg":"頭先去左約睇精神科<br />\n登記個護士問咩事想睇<br />\n我答：「⋯抑鬱？」<br />\n佢再追問有冇食開藥 睇開其他醫生 或者有咩記錄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係唔係唔應該睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該係好嚴重的人先去睇精神科醫生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時未有自殺傾向，以前4-5年前有，不過個時中學生冇錢睇醫生，自己退學返屋企摺咗2年。 慢慢出黎做返野讀返書到依家。 以前最嚴重都從來冇睇過醫生，依家去睇好似好無聊。<br />\n<br />\n不過2年前左右有情緒問題，明顯影響身體。個人3個月肥左20磅，塊面爛曬，個個叫我去睇皮膚科，醫好塊面。跟住食A酸好咗一半，剩低點都唔斷尾。直頭唔理+停A酸，用天然野一輪3-4個月好返曬。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知呢啲叫情緒問題 定 抑鬱<br />\n.......呢幾年呢啲算係長期有抑鬱傾向 定 青春期"},{"pid":"5816f7a1afe38f00fe7e98d93cd134275fb1f53d","tid":754050,"uid":122013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T06:16:17.000Z","msg":"快啲睇，唔怕"},{"pid":"9549776ed408f720f615b66e6c73ecbfa1b35b81","tid":754050,"uid":85420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T07:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed0fb0ca60bcf4bc344cbef7507b13f95c66bc3","tid":754050,"uid":40997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T14:13:06.000Z","msg":"快睇快好 食少啲藥"},{"pid":"5be531b80a50b5d80a844ed0d3b530e7b58db8cb","tid":754050,"uid":106468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T14:25:46.000Z","msg":"好掛住中學 可以同社工傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想有個精神病紀錄所以一直無睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48693413a19a84969f01072f727497e1b83c887","tid":754050,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T15:44:15.000Z","msg":"明顯抑鬱"}]}